_json.gridTitle: Amazing Raised Garden Bed Projects - The Owner-Builder Network
_json.description: Raised garden beds do offer a lot of benefits for gardeners. It makes tending to greens more convenient, especially for people experiencing lower back/knee pain. It could also prevent critters and slugs from ruining produce. Last but not the least, they are a great way to improve landscape. You can choose plain timber to build a garden bed, but there are also many other options to choose from.
